    "2218401": {
      "title": "Targeting microbial biofilms: current and prospective therapeutic strategies",
      "abstract": "In this Review, Stoodley and colleagues discuss current therapeutic strategies and those under development for the treatment of pathogenic biofilms. They explore novel technologies that promise to enhance the efficacy of current therapeutics or provide novel effects and argue that treating biofilm infections requires combination therapies."
    }
